@startuml
title UC09 — Student/Paid User converses with AI — Sequence
actor "Student" as Actor
participant "ConversationPage" as UI
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "AIConversationService" as AIConversationService
database "MySQL" as DB
participant "Anthropic API" as Anthropic_API
participant "ElevenLabs API" as ElevenLabs_API
Actor -> UI : start AI conversation session
UI -> API : HTTPS request
API -> AIConversationService : route and authorize
AIConversationService -> DB : read/write SpeakingSession
DB -->> AIConversationService : data result
AIConversationService -> Anthropic_API : integration request
Anthropic_API -->> AIConversationService : integration response
AIConversationService -> ElevenLabs_API : integration request
ElevenLabs_API -->> AIConversationService : integration response
AIConversationService -->> API : response
API -->> UI : JSON result
UI -->> Actor : AI response and optional audio are returned
@enduml
